<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><a href="http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/File:New_Impress_Templates36.png" class="image" title="Novos modelos."><img src="http://wiki.documentfoundation.org/images/thumb/1/11/New_Impress_Templates36.png/200px-New_Impress_Templates36.png" height="289" alt="Novos modelos." width="200"></a> </span></p>
<h1 style="text-align: justify;"><span class="mw-headline" style="font-size: medium;"> Math </span></h1>
<ul style="text-align: justify;">
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"> As caixas de diálogo para formato (fonte, tamanho da fonte e espaçamento) e símbolo (<strong>Ferramentas-&gt; Catálogo</strong>) agora possuem botões de ajuda. <a href="https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=47860" class="external text" target="_blank">fdo#47860</a>, <a href="https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=47862" class="external text" target="_blank">fdo#47862</a>, <a href="https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=47863" class="external text" target="_blank">fdo#47863</a>, <a href="https://bugs.freedesktop.org/show_bug.cgi?id=47864" class="external text" target="_blank">fdo#47864</a> (Karan Desai) </span></li>
